
External dependencies
=====================
Automatical checking has not been implemented yet :-(

Standard developping tools		gcc, g++, make, makedepend
Drivers for your video card		http://www.nvidia.com/ , http://www.ati.com/
Devel package for SDL			http://www.libsdl.org/
Devel package for SDL_image		http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/
Devel package for SDL_ttf		http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf/


Compile and run
===============
$ cd <project_directory>
$ make clean
$ make depend
$ make
$ vim cfg/basecode.ini
$ make run

